sql:
SELECT username
FROM users
ORDER BY last_login DESC;

external_knowledge:
Here are definitions of terms used in this query: 
- "Most active users" refers to users with the most recent last login and message activity; 
- "Message activity" refers to the latest message sent or received by a user; 
- "Complete profile" means the user has filled out their profile completely.

- 'most messaged users' refers to users who have received the highest number of messages; 
- 'recent activity' means the user has logged in within the last 30 days; 
- 'complete profiles' means users with profile_completion_status = 'complete'.
